X-Ray: Angry Mongolians Smash Abortion Billboards

Russia Today

[URL: http://rt.com/news/fiance-obstetrician-quiet-natalia-032/ - доступ 22.05.2015]

A recently introduced draft law in Mongolia allowing non-medics to carry out abortions has divided opinions in the nation: some openly object to the penetration of foreign values, while others applaud the possible elimination of legal abortions. Some doctors and women are explaining to RT why practices are so out of sync with international medical norms.
